 Phoenix]] ''|| \u601d\u7f8e\u4eba|| [[Qu Yuan]] (young)|| <ref name=song />\n|- \n|''Boy Hood'' || \u6211\u4eec\u7684\u5c11\u5e74\u65f6\u4ee3|| Yin Ke || rowspan=3|Lead role||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cn.chinadaily.com.cn/2017-07/05/content_30006744.htm|title=\u300a\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u5c11\u5e74\u65f6\u4ee3\u300b7\u67089\u65e5\u6e56\u5357\u536b\u89c6\u9996\u64ad TFBOYS\u83b7\u5956\u859b\u4e4b\u8c26\u674e\u5c0f\u7490\u82b1\u5f0f\u4e92\u603c|date=5 July 2018|website=China Daily|language=zh}}</ref> \n|-\n|2019 || ''[[The Longest Day in Chang'an]]'' ||\u957f\u5b89\u5341\u4e8c\u65f6\u8fb0||  Li Bi|| <ref name=long />\n|-\n| 2020 || ''Forward Forever'' || \u70ed\u8840\u540c\u884c|| Ah Yi || <ref name=youth /> \n|-\n|}\n\n=== Web series===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! English title!! Chinese title!! Role !! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes!! Ref.\n|-\n|2013|| ''The Legend of Yunchu Temple'' || \u4e91\u5c45\u5bfa\u4f20\u5947|| Fugui ||\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dailynews.sina.com/bg/chn/chnpolitics/phoenixtv/20130905/19304944583.html|script-title=zh:30\u96c6\u6587\u5316\u7cfb\u5217\u5fae\u96fb\u5f71\u300a\u96f2\u5c45\u5bfa\u50b3\u5947\u300b\u6b63\u5f0f\u4e0a\u7dda|date=5 September 2013|publisher=Sina Corp|language=zh}}</ref>\n|- \n| rowspan=2|2014 || ''Hi-Tech Belle'' || \u9ad8\u79d1\u6280\u5c11\u5973\u55b5|| Lee Kenan's younger brother || rowspan=2|Cameo ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.163.com/14/0613/09/9UK3H3SI00032DGD_mobile.html|script-title=zh:\u6613\u70ca\u5343\u73ba\u5ba2\u4e32\u300a\u9ad8\u79d1\u6280\u5c11\u5973\u55b5\u300b \u5b50\u58a8\"\u6559\u574f\"\u6b63\u592a|work=Netease|date=13 June 2014|language=zh}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Surprise'' ||\u4e07\u4e07\u6ca1\u60f3\u5230\u7b2c\u4e8c\u5b63 || ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/hqcj/xfly/2014-07-08/content_11972223.html|script-title=zh:\u300a\u4e07\u4e072\u300b\u620f\u4eff\u300a\u70ed\u8840\u9ad8\u6821\u300b\u6613\u70ca\u5343\u73ba\u5c55\u5b66\u9738\u672c\u8272|date=4 July 2017|work=